    <p>ED and MAE implemented the algorithm for generating STR profiles. ED, MFB, PAR, MB, and MAE developed methods for comparing STR profiles. PAR performed simulation analyses with guidance from WWW. BT, CN, and RKCY performed confirmatory studies based on long-read data. MFB and PAR curated the catalog of pathogenic repeats. ED, MFB, PAR, BT, SC, JJFAV, CN, GN, VGG, AMG, and BL performed all remaining data analyses. RJT, WWW, SWS, JHV, DRB, RKCY, MB, and MAE supervised and guided the project. ED, MFB, PAR, and MAE wrote the initial draft of the manuscript. The authors read and approved the final manuscript.</p>
